1. *Izaberi* omiljenu pesmu za nas (Choose your favorite song for us)
2. Ja sam *izabrala* ovo odelo za večeras (I chose this outfit for tonight)
3. *Izabran* si da budeš deo tima (You have been chosen to be part of the team)
4. Oni su *izabrali* da putuju vozom umesto autobusom (They chose to travel by train instead of bus)
5. Kandidatkinja koju su *izabrali* je bila veoma kvalifikovana (The candidate they chose was highly qualified)
6. Da li si *izabrao* šta želiš da jedeš? (Have you chosen what you want to eat?)
7. Ova knjiga je bila *izabrana* za nagradu "Najbolja knjiga godine" (This book was selected for the "Best Book of the Year" award)
8. *Izabirući* između dve opcije, odlučila sam se za prvu (Choosing between two options, I decided on the first one)
9. Nakon dužeg razmišljanja, oni su *izabrali* da ne idu na odmor ove godine (After thinking it over, they decided not to go on vacation this year)
10. Molim te da *izabereš* šta želiš da gledamo večeras (Please choose what you want to watch tonight)